  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Dairy</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/32px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n<div><b>“</b><span>A glass of milk with every supper.</span><b>”</b>\n<p>–<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Webber\" title=\"Webber\">Webber</a></p>\n</div>\n<p>There are 3 basic <b>Dairy</b> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Food\" title=\"Food\">food</a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Items\" title=\"Items\">items</a> in-game, none of which have a cooked version.\n</p>\n<div><ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\"><img alt=\"Butter\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Butter.png?313803\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\">Butter</a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electric_Milk\" title=\"Electric Milk\"><img alt=\"Electric Milk\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Electric_Milk.png?4a6d4b\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Electric_Milk\" title=\"Electric Milk\">Electric Milk</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/24px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Milky_Whites\" title=\"Milky Whites\"><img alt=\"Milky Whites\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Milky_Whites.png?882dc5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Milky_Whites\" title=\"Milky Whites\">Milky Whites</a><br><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a></div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul></div>\n<p>There is also 1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crock_Pot\" title=\"Crock Pot\">Crock Pot</a> recipe that requires Dairy products to be made. (There is 1 additional recipe in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Reign of Giants\">Reign of Giants</a></i> DLC <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/24px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a> and 3 additional recipes (and one in which Dairy is optional) in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>.)\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\">Food\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"150px\">Name\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\">DLC\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Hunger_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Hunger\"><img alt=\"Hunger\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hunger_Icon.png/28px-Hunger_Icon.png?9d0486\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Sanity_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sanity\"><img alt=\"Sanity\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sanity_Icon.png/28px-Sanity_Icon.png?eae728\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Health_Icon.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Health\"><img alt=\"Health\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Health_Icon.png/28px-Health_Icon.png?1ec0e6\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Rot.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Perish time (days)\"><img alt=\"Perish time (days)\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Rot.png/28px-Rot.png?31f7bc\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Crock_Pot.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Cook time (sec)\"><img alt=\"Cook time (sec)\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Crock_Pot.png/28px-Crock_Pot.png?8263f1\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\"></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" width=\"0px\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Priority.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Priority\"><img alt=\"Priority\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Priority.png/24px-Priority.png?9a8804\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"></a>\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Recipe\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Requirements*\n</th>\n<th>Filler<br>Restrictions\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\"><img alt=\"Coffee.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Coffee.png/48px-Coffee.png?b20f07\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a></td>\n<td><b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a></b></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>9.375\n</td>\n<td>5\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td>10d\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>30\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Coffee_Beans\" title=\"Roasted Coffee Beans\"><img alt=\"Cooked Coffee Beans.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cooked_Coffee_Beans.png/32px-Cooked_Coffee_Beans.png?2073c5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×3\n</td>\n<td>Only <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dairy_product.png/32px-Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sweetener.png/32px-Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> or <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Roasted_Coffee_Beans\" title=\"Roasted Coffee Beans\"><img alt=\"Cooked Coffee Beans.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Cooked_Coffee_Beans.png/32px-Cooked_Coffee_Beans.png?2073c5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fresh_Fruit_Crepes\" title=\"Fresh Fruit Crepes\"><img alt=\"Fresh Fruit Crepes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fresh_Fruit_Crepes.png/48px-Fresh_Fruit_Crepes.png?bc0640\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a></td>\n<td><b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fresh_Fruit_Crepes\" title=\"Fresh Fruit Crepes\">Fresh Fruit Crepes</a></b></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>150\n</td>\n<td>15\n</td>\n<td>60\n</td>\n<td>10d\n</td>\n<td>20\n</td>\n<td>30\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fruit\" title=\"Fruit\"><img alt=\"Fruit.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fruit.png/32px-Fruit.png?853057\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1.5 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\"><img alt=\"Butter.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Butter.png/32px-Butter.png?313803\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>x1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Honey\" title=\"Honey\"><img alt=\"Honey.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Honey.png/32px-Honey.png?d057e9\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>x1\n</td>\n<td>Cooked in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Portable_Crock_Pot\" title=\"Portable Crock Pot\"><img alt=\"Portable Crock Pot.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Portable_Crock_Pot.png/32px-Portable_Crock_Pot.png?f4c0d3\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\"><img alt=\"Ice Cream.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Ice_Cream.png/48px-Ice_Cream.png?1312fc\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a></td>\n<td><b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice_Cream\" title=\"Ice Cream\">Ice Cream</a></b></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Reign_of_Giants\" title=\"Reign of Giants\"><img alt=\"Reign of Giants icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Reign_of_Giants_icon.png/24px-Reign_of_Giants_icon.png?12c8d5\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>25\n</td>\n<td>50\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>3d\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy_product\" title=\"Dairy product\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dairy_product.png/32px-Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1.0 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Ice.png/32px-Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sweetener\" title=\"Sweetener\"><img alt=\"Sweetener.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Sweetener.png/32px-Sweetener.png?4c4870\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1\n</td>\n<td>No <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Meats.png/32px-Meats.png?6eb40d\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"All Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/All_Eggs.png/32px-All_Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Vegetables\" title=\"Vegetables\"><img alt=\"Veggie.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Veggie.png/32px-Veggie.png?80149d\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Twigs\" title=\"Twigs\"><img alt=\"Twigs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Twigs.png/32px-Twigs.png?2fb15c\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Dinner\" title=\"Lobster Dinner\"><img alt=\"Lobster Dinner.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Lobster_Dinner.png/48px-Lobster_Dinner.png?c5c897\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a></td>\n<td><b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Lobster_Dinner\" title=\"Lobster Dinner\">Wobster Dinner</a></b></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>37.5\n</td>\n<td>50\n</td>\n<td>60\n</td>\n<td>15d\n</td>\n<td>20\n</td>\n<td>25\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wobster\" title=\"Wobster\"><img alt=\"Wobster.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wobster.png/32px-Wobster.png?6460ce\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> (<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked_icon\" title=\"Shipwrecked icon\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/24px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>); <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wobster_(DST)\" title=\"Wobster (DST)\"><img alt=\"Wobster (DST).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Wobster_%28DST%29.png/32px-Wobster_%28DST%29.png?e49d62\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> (<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>)<a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\"><img alt=\"Butter.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Butter.png/32px-Butter.png?313803\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>No <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Meats\" title=\"Meats\"><img alt=\"Meats.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Meats.png/32px-Meats.png?6eb40d\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fishes\" title=\"Fishes\"><img alt=\"Fishes.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Fishes.png/24px-Fishes.png?27fd3c\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\"></a><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ice\" title=\"Ice\"><img alt=\"Ice.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Ice.png/32px-Ice.png?8c6842\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Milkmade_Hat\" title=\"Milkmade Hat\"><img alt=\"Milkmade Hat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Milkmade_Hat.png/48px-Milkmade_Hat.png?552070\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Milkmade_Hat\" title=\"Milkmade Hat\">Milkmade Hat</a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/24px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"24\" height=\"26\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>187.5 in 4 min\n</td>\n<td>-5.3 in 4 min\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td>\n<td>3d\n</td>\n<td>10s\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Naked_Nostrils\" title=\"Naked Nostrils\"><img alt=\"Naked Nostrils.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Naked_Nostrils.png/32px-Naked_Nostrils.png?f797e5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> + <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Kelp_Fronds\" title=\"Kelp Fronds\"><img alt=\"Kelp Fronds.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Kelp_Fronds.png/32px-Kelp_Fronds.png?cb9519\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> + <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy\" title=\"Dairy\"><img alt=\"Dairy product.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dairy_product.png/32px-Dairy_product.png?dcc466\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Waffles\" title=\"Waffles\"><img alt=\"Waffles.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Waffles.png/48px-Waffles.png?dcb4a1\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\"></a></td>\n<td><b><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Waffles\" title=\"Waffles\">Waffles</a></b>\n</td>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td>37.5\n</td>\n<td>5\n</td>\n<td>60\n</td>\n<td>6d\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td>10\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Butter\" title=\"Butter\"><img alt=\"Butter.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Butter.png/32px-Butter.png?313803\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Eggs\" title=\"Eggs\"><img alt=\"All Eggs.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/All_Eggs.png/32px-All_Eggs.png?a3e7ca\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1.0 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Berries\" title=\"Berries\"><img alt=\"Berry.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Berry.png/32px-Berry.png?ddd757\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a>×1\n</td>\n<td>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"tabber tabber--init\"><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Type-0-label\" href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dairy#By_Type-0\">By Type</a><a class=\"tabber__tab\" id=\"By_Crock_P