  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\n“A glass of milk with every supper.”\n–Webber\nThere are 3 basic Dairy food items in-game, none of which have a cooked version.\nButter\nElectric Milk\nMilky Whites\nThere is also 1 Crock Pot recipe that requires Dairy products to be made. (There is 1 additional recipe in the Reign of Giants DLC and 3 additional recipes (and one in which Dairy is optional) in the Shipwrecked DLC .)\nFood\nName\nDLC\nRecipe\nRequirements*\nFiller\nRestrictions\nCoffee\n9.375\n5\n3\n10d\n10\n30\n×3\nOnly or\nFresh Fruit Crepes\n150\n15\n60\n10d\n20\n30\n×1.5 x1 x1\nCooked in\nIce Cream\n25\n50\n0\n3d\n10\n10\n×1.0 ×1 ×1\nNo\nWobster Dinner\n37.5\n50\n60\n15d\n20\n25\n(); ()\nNo\nMilkmade Hat\n187.5 in 4 min\n-5.3 in 4 min\n0\n3d\n10s\n10\n+ +\nWaffles\n37.5\n5\n60\n6d\n10\n10\n×1 ×1.0 ×1\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
