  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Reign of Giants|Shipwrecked|Don't Starve Together}}\n{{Quote|A glass of milk with every supper.|Webber}}\n\nThere are 3 basic '''Dairy''' [[food]] [[items]] in-game, none of which have a cooked version.\n\n<div style=\"clear: both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery position=\"center\" columns=\"6\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nButter.png|link=Butter|[[Butter]]\nElectric Milk.png|link=Electric Milk|[[Electric Milk]]<br>{{pic24|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}}\nFile:Milky Whites.png|link=Milky Whites|[[Milky Whites]]<br>{{DST|24}}\n</gallery></div>\n\nThere is also 1 [[Crock Pot]] recipe that requires Dairy products to be made. (There is 1 additional recipe in the ''[[Reign of Giants]]'' DLC {{pic24|Reign of Giants icon|Reign of Giants}} and 3 additional recipes (and one in which Dairy is optional) in the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC {{pic24|Shipwrecked icon|Shipwrecked}}.)\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight: bold; width:100%\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | Food\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"150px\" | Name\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | DLC\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:HungerMeter.png|28px|Hunger]]\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:SanityMeter.png|28px|Sanity]]\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:HealthMeter.png|28px|Health]]\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:Rot.png|28px|Perish time (days)]]\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:Crock Pot.png|28px|Cook time (sec)]]\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"col\" width=\"0px\" | [[File:Priority.png|24px|Priority]]\n! colspan=\"2\" | Recipe\n|-\n!Requirements*\n!Filler<br />Restrictions\n|-\n|[[File:Coffee.png|48px|link=Coffee]]|| '''[[Coffee]]'''||[[File:Shipwrecked icon.png|24px|link=Shipwrecked]]\n| style=\"background: #ffcc3328\" |9.375\n| style=\"background: #e87b0f28\" |5\n| style=\"background: #ae151528\" |3\n|10d\n|10\n|30\n|[[File:Cooked Coffee Beans.png|32px|link=Roasted Coffee Beans]]×3\n|Only {{pic|32|Dairy product}}{{pic|32|Sweetener}} or [[File:Cooked Coffee Beans.png|32px|link=Roasted Coffee Beans]]\n|-\n|[[File:Fresh Fruit Crepes.png|48px|link=Fresh Fruit Crepes]]|| '''[[Fresh Fruit Crepes]]'''||[[File:Shipwrecked icon.png|24px|link=Shipwrecked]]{{Pic24|Don't Starve Together icon}}\n| style=\"background: #ffcc3328\" |150\n| style=\"background: #e87b0f28\" |15\n| style=\"background: #ae151528\" |60\n|10d\n|20\n|30\n|[[File:Fruit.png|32px|link=Fruit]]×1.5 [[File:Butter.png|32px|link=Butter]]x1 [[File:Honey.png|32px|link=Honey]]x1\n|Cooked in {{pic|32|Portable Crock Pot|link=Portable Crock Pot}}\n|-\n|[[File:Ice Cream.png|48px|link=Ice Cream]]|| '''[[Ice Cream]]'''||[[File:Reign of Giants icon.png|24px|link=Reign of Giants]]\n| style=\"background: #ffcc3328\" |25\n| style=\"background: #e87b0f28\" |50\n| style=\"background: #ae151528\" |0\n|3d\n|10\n|10\n|{{pic|32|Dairy product}}×1.0 {{pic|32|Ice}}×1 [[File:Sweetener.png|32px|link=Sweetener]]×1\n|No [[File:Meats.png|32px|link=Meats]][[File:All Eggs.png|32px|link=Eggs]][[File:Vegetables.png|32px|link=Vegetables]][[File:Twigs.png|32px|link=Twigs]]\n|-\n|[[File:Lobster Dinner.png|48px|link=Lobster Dinner]]|| '''[[Lobster Dinner|Wobster Dinner]]'''||[[File:Shipwrecked icon.png|24px|link=Shipwrecked]]{{Pic24|Don't Starve Together icon}}\n| style=\"background: #ffcc3328\" |37.5\n| style=\"background: #e87b0f28\" |50\n| style=\"background: #ae151528\" |60\n|15d\n|20\n|25\n|[[File:Wobster.png|32px|link=Wobster]] ({{Pic24|Shipwrecked icon}}); {{Pic32|Wobster (DST)}} ({{Pic24|Don't Starve Together icon}})[[File:Butter.png|32px|link=Butter]]\n|No [[File:Meats.png|32px|link=Meats]]{{Pic24|Fishes}}[[File:Ice.png|32px|link=Ice]]\n|-\n| {{Pic|48|Milkmade Hat}}\n| [[Milkmade Hat]]\n| {{DST|24}}\n| style=\"backgrou